scripts.build: npm run build:dev && npm run build:production
scripts.footprint: npm run footprint:dev && npm run footprint:production
scripts.min: npm run min:dev && npm run min:production
scripts.min:dev: cd dist && uglifyjs system.src.js -cm --source-map content=system.src.js.map --comments "/SystemJS v/" -o system.js
scripts.min:production: cd dist && uglifyjs system-production.src.js -cm --source-map content=system-production.src.js.map --comments "/SystemJS v/" -o system-production.js
scripts.prepublish: rimraf dist && npm run build && npm run min
scripts.test: npm run test:production && npm run test:babel && npm run test:traceur
